ACADEMIC / NON-CLINICAL USE NOTICE
----------------------------------
CareAttend is an academic project produced for the COM668 Computing Project
module at Ulster University. It is a research and educational demonstrator and
is NOT certified, validated, or licensed for clinical, diagnostic, or commercial
use. Its predictions must not be used to make real patient-care decisions. The
models are trained on synthetic, NHS-style data only — no real patient data is
used or stored.
